    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そもそも、見物って何の見物に来たんだい、
こんな何もない廃墟にさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>To begin with, what king of sightseeing were you exactly planning to come here for? These are nothing but ruins, after all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私、歴史建造物とか見て
歩くのが趣味なんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, I'm pretty interested in whatever historical evidence I can find here! Simple as that!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなの初耳だぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>First time hearing you say you like history.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私も初知りだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>First time I found out myself!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43748</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……で？　本当は何しに来たんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Really? ...Tell us the truth, why are you here?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43812</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>例えば……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For example...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>例えば？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For example...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>逆に～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>On the other hand...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>逆に？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>On the other hand?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もしかしたら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But maybe...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんで、そんなに言いたくないんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's all this playing around the bush speak!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44244</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ミステリアスな女は魅力的だって
言うからね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mystery is part of a woman's charm, you know!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ため息つくと、
幸せが逃げちゃうよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Such a happy-sounding sigh you both have!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_059_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>誰だよ、ため息つかせてんのは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who are you? Who can think a sigh can be happy..!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
